.DT
query_read_short
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_read_short

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_read_short -  This method returns the short description to use with the reading.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_read_short(object player,
int dummy)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the player reading the message

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/read_desc.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the short description to use with the reading.
It will go: You read <read short>: 

It will automaticly add a $name$ onto the end of the string for you. This will be replaced with the correct a/the short for the message which is printed.
.EP

